♪The wind drifts alone and free♪

00:09:44.989 --> 00:09:48.037
♪Through seasons, none asks of me♪

00:09:50.085 --> 00:09:52.908
♪Spring fades, and autumn wails♪

00:09:54.149 --> 00:09:57.656
♪Only the waning moon
lights my solitude♪

00:09:59.429 --> 00:10:02.083
♪Love arose with the wind's sigh♪

00:10:03.498 --> 00:10:07.150
♪On a cold night,
a swan's shadow flashes by♪

00:10:08.613 --> 00:10:10.341
♪You're deeply devoted♪

00:10:10.944 --> 00:10:15.173
♪Yet spring wind betrayed your heart♪

00:10:16.709 --> 00:10:20.293
♪I miss you so much♪

00:10:20.293 --> 00:10:21.445
♪I never forget you♪

00:10:22.021 --> 00:10:25.317
♪A brief period of love-sickness♪

00:10:25.989 --> 00:10:28.837
♪You won my heart over♪

00:10:28.837 --> 00:10:31.216
♪Why did we first meet♪

00:10:31.216 --> 00:10:35.077
♪Seeking spring's song
and night whispers♪

00:10:35.077 --> 00:10:38.117
♪Long autumn comes,
and wild geese southward fly♪

00:10:38.117 --> 00:10:40.999
♪The azure clouds know my name♪

00:10:40.999 --> 00:10:44.421
♪I remember you, and you understand me♪

00:10:44.421 --> 00:10:47.269
♪Watching the sun set♪

00:10:47.381 --> 00:10:50.245
♪Autumn departs, and beauty fades away♪

00:10:50.245 --> 00:10:54.437
♪To lean on you once more someday♪